    <entry>
      <title>Kali2023安装Nessus</title>
      <link href="/posts/d1923e7c.html"/>
      <url>/posts/d1923e7c.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Kali-2023-安装-Nessus"><a href="#Kali-2023-安装-Nessus" class="headerlink" title="Kali 2023 安装 Nessus"></a>Kali 2023 安装 Nessus</h1><h2 id="一、下载"><a href="#一、下载" class="headerlink" title="一、下载"></a>一、下载</h2><p>在Kali中访问Nessus官网下载对应的系统安装包</p><p>Nessus官网：<a href="https://www.tenable.com/downloads/nessus?loginAttempted=true">https://www.tenable.com/downloads/nessus?loginAttempted=true</a></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Zhianl/picture@main/image-20231121230432479.png" alt=" "></p><h2 id="二、安装"><a href="#二、安装" class="headerlink" title="二、安装"></a>二、安装</h2><p>为了方便，在root目录新建一个Nessus文件夹.</p><p>下载完成后，执行以下命令安装。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">dpkg -i Nessus-10.6.3-debian10_amd64.deb </code></pre><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Zhianl/picture@main/image-20231124103356871.png"></p><h2 id="三、启动"><a href="#三、启动" class="headerlink" title="三、启动"></a>三、启动</h2><p>安装完成后，启动Nessus服务.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">systemctl start nessusd.service</code></pre><p>&nbsp;</p><p>访问 <a href="https://kali:8834/">https://kali:8834/</a> 进入安装页面，选择continue。</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Zhianl/picture@main/8e3d4b4ded53a3b38afa1625503f7cbd430579369.png%401256w_672h_!web-article-pic.avif"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>选择 Link Nessus to another Tenable product 离线部署，Continue；</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Zhianl/picture@main/9d4825e9b177627cf268ff02dad6651b430579369.png%401256w_672h_!web-article-pic.avif"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>选择 tenable.sc，Continue。</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Zhianl/picture@main/f840692313a27d2e65ad2972211600ab430579369.png%401256w_672h_!web-article-pic.avif"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>然后设置用户名和密码，然后Submit，等待配置完成。</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Zhianl/picture@main/image-20231121234926713.png"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Zhianl/picture@main/image-20231121235006929.png"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>安装完成，因为是离线安装，所以很多插件都没有下载。</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Zhianl/picture@main/image-20231121235229663.png"></p><h2 id="四、离线激活"><a href="#四、离线激活" class="headerlink" title="四、离线激活"></a>四、离线激活</h2><p>访问官网注册账户获取注册码，注册码会发到你填的邮箱中。</p><p>注册页面：<a href="https://zh-cn.tenable.com/tenable-for-education/nessus-essentials?edu=true">https://zh-cn.tenable.com/tenable-for-education/nessus-essentials?edu=true</a></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Zhianl/picture@main/image-20231121233405462.png"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>打开邮箱查看注册码，注册码只能使用一次。</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Zhianl/picture@main/image-20231121233702309.png"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>输入以下命令获取challenge码</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">/opt/nessus/sbin/nessuscli fetch --challenge</code></pre><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Zhianl/picture@main/image-20231121234110056.png"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>然后访问：<a href="https://plugins.nessus.org/v2/offline.php">https://plugins.nessus.org/v2/offline.php</a> ，输入challenge码和注册码进行激活。</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Zhianl/picture@main/image-20231121234308787.png"></p><p>提交后官方会给出插件的下载地址和激活证书，然后复制链接地址到新窗口下载。</p><p>如果直接点击下载，页面跳转后激活证书会失效。</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Zhianl/picture@main/image-20231121235514720.png"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Zhianl/picture@main/image-20231121235653434.png"></p><p>下载后，将插件和证书放到Nessus目录下。</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Zhianl/picture@main/image-20231121235852941.png"></p><h2 id="五、安装插件"><a href="#五、安装插件" class="headerlink" title="五、安装插件"></a>五、安装插件</h2><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">/opt/nessus/sbin/nessuscli update ./all-2.0.tar.gz</code></pre><p>&nbsp;</p><p>提示 Update successful 即插件更新成功。</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Zhianl/picture@main/image-20231122000359650.png"></p><h2 id="六、安装证书"><a href="#六、安装证书" class="headerlink" title="六、安装证书"></a>六、安装证书</h2><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">/opt/nessus/sbin/nessuscli fetch --register-offline nessus.license</code></pre><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Zhianl/picture@main/9e75609513a7edffec776a764c474084430579369.png%401256w_712h_!web-article-pic.avif"></p><h2 id="七、重启Nessus"><a href="#七、重启Nessus" class="headerlink" title="七、重启Nessus"></a>七、重启Nessus</h2><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">systemctl restart nessusd</code></pre><p>&nbsp;</p><p>等待更新完成。</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Zhianl/picture@main/236cb330e7879da6aaa8f3f003179c09430579369.png%401256w_672h_!web-article-pic.avif"></p><p>加载完成后，输入之前设置的账号密码进行登录。</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Zhianl/picture@main/image-20231122001029804.png"></p><p>等待插件编译完成</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Zhianl/picture@main/image-20231122000858088.png"></p><h2 id="八、编译过程中遇到的问题"><a href="#八、编译过程中遇到的问题" class="headerlink" title="八、编译过程中遇到的问题"></a>八、编译过程中遇到的问题</h2><h3 id="1、磁盘内存不足"><a href="#1、磁盘内存不足" class="headerlink" title="1、磁盘内存不足"></a>1、磁盘内存不足</h3><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Zhianl/picture@main/image-20231124133856812.png"></p><h3 id="2、解决方法：添加磁盘空间"><a href="#2、解决方法：添加磁盘空间" class="headerlink" title="2、解决方法：添加磁盘空间"></a>2、解决方法：添加磁盘空间</h3><p>瞬间穿越，探索未知领域！<a href="/posts/6e71f53.html" title="Kali 增加磁盘空间">Kali 增加磁盘空间</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
